 combination of 樹懶 \'\'namakemono\'\' (sloth) and なまける \'\'namakeru\'\' (slack off).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Normal|type2=Normal\n|ja=ナマケロ \'\'Namakero\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|樹懶 \'\'namakemono\'\'|sloth}}\n|fr=Parecool|frmeaning=From {{tt|\'\'paresseux\'\'|sloth}} and \'\'cool\'\'\n|es=Slakoth|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Bummelz|demeaning=From {{tt|\'\'bummeln\'\'|to slack}} and {{tt|\'\'Faulpelz\'\'|sloth bear}}\n|it=Slakoth|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=게을로 \'\'Geulro\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|게으르다 \'\'ge\'eureuda\'\'|to be lazy}}, {{tt|게을리 \'\'ge\'eulli\'\'|lazily, idly}}\n|zh_cmn=懶人翁 / 懒人翁 \'\'Lǎnrénwēng\'\' |zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|樹懶 \'\'shùlǎn\'\'|sloth}}, {{tt|懶人 \'\'lǎnrén\'\'|lazy man}}, and {{tt|懶翁 \'\'lǎnwēng\'\'|slacker}}\n|ru=Слакот \'\'Slakot\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Normal}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Normal|prevnum=286|prev=Breloom|nextnum=288|next=Vigoroth}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Bummelz]]\n[[es:Slakoth]]\n[[fr:Parecool]]\n[[it:Slakoth]]\n[[ja:ナマケロ]]\n[[zh:懒人獭]]'}